# Environment Variables Configuration

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your API keys:

```env
# ============================================
# WHAPI (WhatsApp Gateway)
# ============================================
# Your WHAPI authentication token
WHAPI_TOKEN=your_whapi_token_here

# WHAPI base URL (do not change)
WHAPI_URL=https://gate.whapi.com

# Recipient phone number (international format, no + sign)
WHATSAPP_RECIPIENT=34600000000

# ============================================
# GROQ AI (Summarization)
# ============================================
# Get your API key at: https://console.groq.com/
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# ============================================
# RENDER DEPLOYMENT
# ============================================
# Do not change this (used by Render free tier)
PORT=8080
```

## How to get your API keys

### WHAPI Token
1. Sign up at https://whapi.com/
2. Go to Dashboard → API Keys
3. Copy your authentication token

### Groq API Key
1. Sign up at https://console.groq.com/
2. Go to API Keys → Create Key
3. Copy your API key (use `gsk_` prefix)

## Security Notice
- **Never commit `.env` to version control**
- Add `.env` to your `.gitignore`
- Use different keys for production vs development